title: DarkHorse Podcast with Tristan Harris & Bret Weinstein
description:
Tristan is the Co-Founder and President of the Center for Humane Technology, and Co-Host of podcast "Your Undivided Attention". 

Find Tristan on Your Undivided Attention: https://www.humanetech.com/podcast 
Find Tristan on Twitter: @tristanharris 

Theme Music: Thank you to Martin Molin of Wintergatan for providing us the rights to use their excellent music. 

Support the show (https://www.patreon.com/bretweinstein)
